(1. Introduction) Tj
0 -13 Td
(The Quiz Automation Platform is a web-based system designed to simplify quiz creation, improve quiz evaluation speed, and provide meaningful learning analytics for college teaching environments. The platform enables teachers to generate and manage MCQs \\(including AI-assisted question generation\\) while students can attempt quizzes in a timed and structured manner.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(A key objective of this project is to make teaching analytics decision-ready. After a quiz is submitted, the teacher can analyze student performance through a dashboard that highlights:) Tj
0 -13 Td
(- The top performer in the quiz \\(overall ranking\\).) Tj
0 -13 Td
(- Top 3 students stream-wise.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(- Top 3 students area/region-wise.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(To support academic integrity during live attempts, the platform integrates an anti-cheating logging mechanism and provides teacher-visible logs. The system also includes gamification \\(XP, levels, badges\\) to improve student engagement and consistency.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(Core workflow:) Tj
0 -13 Td
(1\\) Secure signup/login for teachers and students.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(2\\) Teacher quiz creation and AI question generation with review/approval.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(3\\) Student timed quiz attempts.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(4\\) Automatic evaluation and instant results.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(5\\) Teacher dashboards with quiz analytics and top-3 segmented rankings.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
